steps.name: I login to the fusion application using the "RP_FA_Accountant" role
I click on the "Fixed Assets" option in the Navigator
I click on "Assets" from the "Fixed Assets" Dropdown
I should see "Assets" Page
I create an asset
I click on the "Adjust Assets" from the Task Panel
I should see "Adjust Assets" Page
I search for the asset to be modified
search result will be displayed
I select the asset and click on "Change Financial Details" button
I should see "Change Financial Details:" Page
I update details for Cost
I click on the "Submit" button
